{"article_id":"gLIS95tx0E4NgewU","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"A Tennessee woman","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"serving life in prison for the 2004 murder of a man","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"who solicited her for sex as a girl","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"has been granted clemency .","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"Tennessee Governor Bill Haslam ordered the release of Cyntoia Brown , 30 , after almost 15 years behind bars .","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"She was tried as an adult and convicted in 2006 for murdering a Nashville estate agent","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"when she was 16 .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"Prosecutors said","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"it was robbery .","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"Brown said","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"she was a child sex-trafficking victim","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"who fired in self-defence .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"Her case drew support from celebrities like singer Rihanna , reality TV personality Kim Kardashian West , comedian Amy Schumer and NBA star LeBron James .","depth":4},{"id":13,"text":"Brown 's incarceration was the subject of the 2011 documentary Me Facing Life :","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"Cyntoia 's Story .","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"She told the film-makers","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"that she was picked up in Nashville by a 43-year-old estate agent , Johnny Allen ,","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"who agreed to pay her $ 150","depth":13},{"id":18,"text":"to have sex","depth":13},{"id":19,"text":"and drove her to his home .","depth":12},{"id":20,"text":"But she said","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"that once at Allen 's home , he groped her roughly","depth":12},{"id":22,"text":"and then rolled over","depth":13},{"id":23,"text":"to reach the side of the bed .","depth":13},{"id":24,"text":"Brown said","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"she feared","depth":13},{"id":26,"text":"he was going to get a gun","depth":13},{"id":27,"text":"so she shot him .","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"Prosecutors at the time alleged","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"that she killed the victim","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"as he was sleeping ,","depth":12},{"id":31,"text":"and stole his money , guns and lorry","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"before fleeing the scene .","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"They claimed","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"that she was motivated by greed ,","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"but her defence lawyers argued","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"that she was afraid of returning home empty-handed to her violent pimp ,","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"who went by the nickname Kutthroat .","depth":12},{"id":38,"text":"After entering a plea of self-defence ,","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"a jury found her guilty of first-degree premeditated murder , first-degree felony murder and aggravated robbery .","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"In a statement on Monday , the state 's Republican governor said","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"he had ordered","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"that Brown be released to parole supervision on 7 August this year .","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"`` Cyntoia Brown committed , by her own admission , a horrific crime at the age of 16 , ''","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"the statement said .","depth":10},{"id":45,"text":"`` Yet , imposing a life sentence on a juvenile","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"that would require her to serve at least 51 years","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"before even being eligible for parole consideration","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"is too harsh , especially in light of the extraordinary steps","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"Ms Brown has taken","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"to rebuild her life .","depth":13},{"id":51,"text":"Nashville Mayor David Briley called the decision a `` great day for social justice and our city '' .","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"Brown ,","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"who has earned an associate degree while in prison ,","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"said","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"she would do everything","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"to justify Governor Haslam 's faith in her .","depth":7},{"id":57,"text":"`` I am thankful for all the support , prayers and encouragement","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"I have received , ''","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"she said in a statement .","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"`` We truly serve a God of second chances and new beginnings .","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"`` The Lord has held my hand this whole time","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"and I would never have made it","depth":9},{"id":63,"text":"without Him . ''","depth":9},{"id":64,"text":"She will be eligible for release on 7 August ,","depth":4},{"id":65,"text":"after serving 15 years behind bars .","depth":4},{"id":66,"text":"After the announcement was made ,","depth":3},{"id":67,"text":"Kim Kardashian West tweeted her thanks .","depth":3},{"id":68,"text":"Actresses Alyssa Milano and Sophia Bush were also among the celebrities","depth":4},{"id":69,"text":"voicing their support on Twitter .","depth":4},{"id":70,"text":"Stacey Abrams ,","depth":6},{"id":71,"text":"who ran as the first black female nominee for governor in the US during the mid-term elections ,","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"said","depth":5},{"id":73,"text":"the victory belonged to Brown and the activists","depth":5},{"id":74,"text":"`` who refused to concede injustice '' .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":149,"left":140,"right":148,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":140,"left":87,"right":139,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":87,"left":79,"right":86,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":79,"left":78,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":78,"left":77,"right":3,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":77,"left":0,"right":76,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":86,"left":85,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":85,"left":82,"right":84,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"